    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      534.58,
      38.16,
      542.6,
      49.2
    ],
    "text": "3",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      87.11,
      543.44,
      102.65
    ],
    "text": "by the Respondents. This court by its order dated 10.2.2012 granted leave to",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      111.23,
      497.77,
      126.77
    ],
    "text": "proceed for alleged violation of Article 12(1) and 13(1) of the Constitution.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      135.35,
      543.03,
      150.89
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner, in April 1975, joined the Sri Lanka Army as a soldier and in1985",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      157.6,
      543.22,
      175.13
    ],
    "text": "was promoted to the 7th Military Intelligence Unit as a Lance Corporal. In 2003 he",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      183.71,
      542.98,
      199.25
    ],
    "text": "left the Sri Lanka Army without permission. In 2006 he was apprehended by the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      207.83,
      543.15,
      223.37
    ],
    "text": "Sri Lanka Army and was sent to Singha Regiment in Nuwara Eliya. During the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      231.98,
      543.25,
      247.52
    ],
    "text": "period commencing from 2003 to 2006 he worked as a lorry driver. On 27.2.2010,",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      254.23,
      543.6,
      271.76
    ],
    "text": "the officers of the Terrorist Investigations Division (TID) led by the 5th Respondent",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      280.34,
      542.94,
      295.88
    ],
    "text": "arrested the Petitioner informing him that they wanted to record a statement from",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      304.46,
      543.32,
      320.0
    ],
    "text": "him. The Petitioner states that he was not informed of the reasons for his arrest. At",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      328.58,
      543.61,
      344.12
    ],
    "text": "the Criminal Investigation Department (CID), he was asked whether he knew a",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      352.82,
      543.25,
      368.36
    ],
    "text": "person by the name of Pitchchai Jesudasan. As he could not recollect the name of",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      376.94,
      543.56,
      392.48
    ],
    "text": "such person, he was shown a photograph of a person said to be Pitchchai",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      401.08,
      546.56,
      416.62
    ],
    "text": "Jesudasan. The Petitioner then identified the person in the photograph as Das. Das",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      425.2,
      543.4,
      440.74
    ],
    "text": "was a motor mechanic in Nuwara Eliya. He (the Petitioner) explained to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      449.44,
      543.59,
      464.98
    ],
    "text": "officers of the TID when he was working as a lorry driver, he used to take his lorry",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      473.56,
      543.01,
      489.1
    ],
    "text": "to Das\u2019s garage for repairs and that on some occasions he had consumed liquor",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      497.68,
      543.22,
      513.22
    ],
    "text": "with Das. The Petitioner further states that he was questioned with regard to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      521.8,
      543.08,
      537.34
    ],
    "text": "murder of Lasantha Wickramatunga. On 26.5.2010 he was produced before the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      545.95,
      543.24,
      561.49
    ],
    "text": "Magistrate\u2019s Court, Colombo and was transferred to the Remand Prison. He has",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      570.19,
      542.9,
      585.73
    ],
    "text": "produced a copy of the case record of the Magistrate\u2019s Court as P1 and a copy of",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      594.31,
      543.02,
      609.85
    ],
    "text": "the detention order as P2. On 10.11.2010 he was discharged from the proceedings",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      618.43,
      543.41,
      633.97
    ],
    "text": "in the Magistrate\u2019s Court (MC Colombo B 4855/8/2010) on the basis that no",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      642.55,
      543.42,
      658.09
    ],
    "text": "further legal action would be pursued against him. Pitchchai Jesudasan too was",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      666.79,
      543.41,
      682.33
    ],
    "text": "discharged on the same basis. The Petitioner states although he was discharged",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      690.93,
      543.5,
      706.47
    ],
    "text": "from the proceedings in the Magistrate\u2019s Court, Colombo, he was added as a",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      715.05,
      543.07,
      730.59
    ],
    "text": "suspect to the proceedings in the Magistrate\u2019s Court Mount Lavinia B 92/2009",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      534.58,
      38.16,
      542.6,
      49.2
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      87.11,
      543.15,
      102.65
    ],
    "text": "regarding the murder of Lasantha Wickramatunga. The Petitioner states that his",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      111.23,
      543.09,
      126.77
    ],
    "text": "arrest and detention are illegal and that his arrest and detention constitute",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      135.35,
      543.61,
      150.89
    ],
    "text": "continuing infringement of his fundamental rights guaranteed Article 12(1) and",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      159.59,
      217.88,
      175.13
    ],
    "text": "13(1) of the Constitution.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      181.72,
      543.15,
      199.25
    ],
    "text": "The 2nd Respondent who is in charge of the Terrorist Investigation Division",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      207.83,
      543.55,
      223.37
    ],
    "text": "of the CID in his affidavit states that the investigation which was conducted by",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      231.98,
      543.16,
      247.52
    ],
    "text": "Mirihana Police regarding the murder of Lasantha Wickramatunga was",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      256.22,
      543.11,
      271.76
    ],
    "text": "subsequently handed over to the CID on 17.12.2009; that Lasantha Wickramatunga",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      280.34,
      542.98,
      295.88
    ],
    "text": "had received telephone calls from five mobile numbers prior to his death; that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      304.46,
      543.57,
      320.0
    ],
    "text": "Sim Cards pertaining to the said mobile numbers had been purchased by a person",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      328.58,
      543.01,
      344.12
    ],
    "text": "holding National Identity Card (NIC) number 711713050V; that the investigation",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      352.82,
      542.95,
      368.36
    ],
    "text": "had revealed that said NIC belongs to one Pitchchai Jesudasan of Nuwara Eliya;",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      376.94,
      543.27,
      392.48
    ],
    "text": "that when Pitchchai Jesudasan was arrested it was revealed that he had lost his NIC",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      401.08,
      542.88,
      416.62
    ],
    "text": "in 2008; that the said Sim Cards had been purchased subsequent to the loosing of",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      425.2,
      543.15,
      440.74
    ],
    "text": "his NIC; that the investigation had revealed that Pitchchai Jesudasan had lost his",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      449.44,
      543.34,
      464.98
    ],
    "text": "wallet after he consumed liquor with the Petitioner in August 2008; that acting on",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      473.56,
      542.97,
      489.1
    ],
    "text": "this information the Petitioner was arrested on 27.2.2010; and that the said Sim",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      497.68,
      543.3,
      513.22
    ],
    "text": "Cards had been purchased from a communication centre which was situated",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      521.8,
      543.48,
      537.34
    ],
    "text": "opposite the Military Camp where the Petitioner was attached to. The officer who",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      545.95,
      543.61,
      561.49
    ],
    "text": "arrested the Petitioner has not filed an affidavit in this court. Arresting notes had",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      568.2,
      543.39,
      585.73
    ],
